title: 228: 10 Takeaways from Week 9
itunes:title: 228: 10 Takeaways from Week 9
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks share their ten biggest takeaways from Week 9. Topics include: the exceptional play of quarterbacks Jared Goff and Carson Wentz (3:45), the Denver Broncos' issues at quarterback (16:15), the New Orleans Saints establishing themselves as contenders in the NFC (18:50), and more.
